76561198017127010,Recommended,271240,28499075,"Posted: 20 December, 2016",all,chaogoesmu,"I've been staring at this game since early alpha debating whether to buy it and finally bit the bullet.  I should have done this when it was first offered.  If you like the idea of a super fast paced game of domination that is different every time, buy this.  Every thing you do can be countered by your opponent, and likewise you can counter everything your opponent does.  actions per minute helps but isn't necessary; playing smart is infinitely more important.  Every action your opponents take will have direct consequences on your products and prices, can you figure out what the demand is going to be?  will you be caught in a competitive market with your profits steadily dropping?  Will you just dominate through overproduction of your opponents?  Will you lock down technology that lets you skip their profit margins and go directly back into your product?  Will you find a niche that no one is competing in and exploit it?  There are so many paths to victory or defeat in this game and its so simple yet complex at the same time.  If you are still on the fence watch a few lets play videos until you get the gist of it, then figure out how the patent lab, off world market, blackmarket etc. make it infinitely more intricate.  Minutes to learn, lifetime to master.  Excellent game design."
