76561197994137432,Recommended,271240,22986665,"Posted: 14 May, 2016",all,Confused,"This is a great game. It is incredibly hard to figure out on your own so I highly recommend watching a Twitch tutorial. You also want to learn with the pause button (space bar) pretty much constantly on. Good players can crush it in a couple of minutes so consider yourself warned.I love that every choice can hurt you or help you in a logical way. If you build a dozen farms it will drive up the price on water to keep them going. If you sell goods cheaply they only get cheaper, so it is time to make something else. If you can see the impact of your actions you can manipulate the market in cool ways (e.g. using a robotics company that requires no water to create a water shortage can cripple your fleshy foes).The AI is pretty good and it rarely makes outright terrible errors. This means that even the tutorials can be punishingly hard if you are not paying attention. The music is beautiful and the tempo builds as the match progresses giving you a real rush at the end.Play it."
