76561197969379687,Recommended,271240,14470039,"Posted: 14 February, 2015",all,Fignuts,"Even in alpha, this game is already excellent and challenging. Plus, there's so much more the develpers (and modders) could do with it.It has that rush RTS feel the entire game, with a great blend of strategy (choosing which resources to focus on, which research to do, which kind of ecomony to focus on, considering which faction you are) and tactics (black market sabotage, market manipulations, and selling/buying strategies). It may not look like it from the screenshots, but you feel like you're in constant combat with your opponents.Economic and market considtions are constantly changing based on the given map's resources and player/AI behavior; however, it doesn't change so fast that you can't find trends and predict how resource demand will change and make decisive, bold moves to crush opponents.I see a near-limitless potential for deep strategy, counter-strategy and evolving meta-strategies for this game. Extremely excited to see where this game goes!"
