,Not Recommended,271240,24220796,"Posted: 9 July, 2016",all,Tanelorn,"I put in my time with this game and really enjoyed the tutorial missions. However, once you try against bots higher than ""newbie"" level, the game becomes impossible.This game also fails to be about economic competition, really. You are very handicapped in the information available to you so you can't really read the markets or predict other player's stances. The most powerful competitive edge given players in this game are special attacks you purchase from the black market. With these you can freeze their structures, blow them up, take them over, etc. That's where the most manipulation comes in. The game is really about breaking even then using sabotage to get the advantage.I wanted to like this game but now I despise it. There also should be a turn based mode to remove the ""i can micro better than you"" element that so many RTS games have. There's no reason why this couldn't be a fun turn based game it's set up perfectly for it."
