 both lag.Man I wish I had my degree already, so I could get hired by companies like this to fix their games for them. I'm not arrogant, but damn like how hard is it to make a game like this correctly. It's barely 3d, no combat, just numbers and sprites.The AI is probably one massive set of If..Else statements, IN A LOOP. gawd.Great concept, terrible deployment. So far. I will wait for the final release."
