76561197966526680,Recommended,271240,26039358,"Posted: 14 October, 2016",all,Saracen26,"So Offworld Trading Company and me have had this ""thing"" for a very long time. I love RTS, always have since the mid 90's. I also love innovative games, well since games have existed. So when this game was announced, I watched and followed it like a hawk. Except I kept and maintained my distance. OTC was like a woman I'd see in a bar every week, it seemed love at first sight. She was beautiful, intriguing, like no-one I'd ever seen before.. But alas I was always drunk when I saw her and I had no courage to approach her, buy her a drink, get her number, maybe take her home.It was like this for months. The more I found out about her, the more character that she seemed to divulge, the more personality she put on display, the more I wanted her. Moving up the ranks in my little black book known as a wishlist. The more I came to the bar, the more she'd flash (sale), the more of her clothing (Price tag) she'd remove. It was at this point, I knew she was flirting with me, and it became apparent she's was now bundled in gold. So a weekend in mid-October she returned to the bar wearing 65% off... This time I was not drunk, I was no longer on the fence... I saw her for what she was, so after flashing my credit card, I finally took her home.After a 6 hour session with her... I have to say, she's rather intense. She showed me the ropes, showed me the many facets of her personality and showed me step by step what made her tick. Then she untied me and let me get to work on her...At first she was easy. I kept winning her charms, satisfying her needs... Things were going smoothly, she allowed me to tackle a single element of her, and then she ramped things up, adding more and more, asking for more and more. Things began to get more and more intense... Then she showed her true colours. The more you play her, the more she dares to push you. She becomes a shady, manipulative, dirty scheming devil woman who will push you into a corner, pin you there, and drain you economically for all you're worth.The thing is. You will not learn to back down. She leaves you wanting more, she wants to be dominated. Taken control of, but she isn't going to let you have it without a fight. In my case on a couple of occassions, she's kept up with me with everything I throw at her, and just when I'm about to get the upper hand, she will kick me down and laugh in my face... I should be humiliated. But I cannot get enough of her. I will keep going for the long-term until our relationship is exhausted. Until she has no more to give and finally submits to my own superior evil ways.. Just like she taught me...Offworld Trading Company... The game is indeed like a woman who wears the trousers, makes all the rules, is controlling of you... But wow, what a woman she is... My only regret is that I didn't take her home sooner."
