,Recommended,271240,29020699,Posted: 4 January,all,Joker,"The game is what i would call a ""Small MasterPiece""Its a rare game to be honest.Its a bit diferent from other games as well.You build your own Company and start building factories that bring in Resources so you can sell them, but you have to watch the market prices all the time since they go up and down.Something Important that not even i knew when i first baught the game.This game isnt a continues build company. Like for example you start a game (Single Player) and you build and build and create more and more. At least thats what i though in the begining. No.This game is a PvP sort of game. You join a lobby wait for players to join in and then you start the game. What you have to do is build correctly your business, bring in necesary resources so you can upgrade your HQ so you can build more. Buy stock of other players which a player has 10 slots of stock. Buy 5 slots of stock and then you can buy all his company and throw him out of the game. Build what sells more. Watch your money rise. Be the last man standing and win.Basically every match lasts a maximum 20 minutes. Its not a continues game and has no story. So if you are a person who wants a calm relaxing game that asks you to build a company by going around gatherind Resources to build and grow then you are at the wrong place.I give the game as a game    (9/10*)But since it has very little players and all you do mostly is play with AI Skyrmish im giving it an    (8/10*)If it had more people for sure i would give it    (9.5/10*)"
